  "title": "Childcare Cook/Cleaner(Full Time)  Tampines (MRT)",
  "description": "<h5>Job Description &amp; Requirements</h5>\n<p>Cook cum cleaner at Childcare Centre in Tampines near the MRT</p>\n<p>To prepare breakfast, lunch and tea break.</p>\n<p>To maintain cleanliness in the kitchen, storeroom and to take charge of groceries.</p>\n<p>Must clean the workplace and follow heath and safet guidlines.</p>\n<p>To follow all sanitation procedures.</p>\n<p>Work as a team with the cleaners.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>7 - 4.30 pm / 8-5pm</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Call Cecilia at 90690910</strong></p>",
